{"tid":1960003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美軍衛生首長警告：本週係「珍珠港」及「911」時刻","createTime":"2020-04-06T00:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T12:39:10.000Z","uid":305299,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f865fb5839982b7dfe93c82fdec81eb66f0c509a","tid":1960003,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T00:09:04.000Z","msg":"美國官方用「珍珠港」同「911」字眼來形容，係好大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係唔知美國疫後會點同中國計依筆數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=====<br />\n美軍衛生首長 (Surgeon General) 向全國國民警告，來緊一個禮拜將會係大多數美國人生命中最艱難同最難過嘅時刻。<br />\n<br />\n衛生首長 Jerome Adams 表示：「依個會係我地嘅珍珠港時刻，係我地 9/11 時刻，而且唔係地區性，而係全國性四圍爆發，我希望美國人能夠明白依一點。」佢同時呼籲各州州長，如果仲未下達居家令嘅話，應該要好好考慮下令，即使係好短暫時間都好。佢表示：「如果畀唔到我地一個月嘅時間，就畀我地一個禮拜時間，畀到幾多得幾多。」<br />\n<br />\n美國衛生首長係負責掌管美軍八支制服軍種入面嘅公共衛生服務軍官團，主要任務係保護，促進同增進美國公眾嘅健康同安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2020/04/05/politics/jerome-adams-coronavirus/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2Fpolitics%2Fjerome-adams-coronavirus%2Findex.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=a776efac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2Fpolitics%2Fjerome-adams-coronavirus%2Findex.html&h=2175740e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/04/05/politics/jerome-adams-coronavirus/index.html</a><br />\nSurgeon General: This week will be like a 'Pearl Harbor' and '9/11' moment"},{"pid":"e4bd8c0cec5b5c06274e026bd2aef1b3d394b598","tid":1960003,"uid":308595,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T00:10:53.000Z","msg":"美國完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3cc484a745494daf2cbef3f0075cca58c3afef","tid":1960003,"uid":82779,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"quote":{"pi